data.description: Wonderful natural stone and brick 3, 2.5 home is situated on a spacious 2.5 acre lot, allowing you to create your own personal oasis. NO CITY TAXES- Located on outskirts of Waxahachie, close to Maypearl area with rolling hills and gorgeous countryside. Step inside and be greeted by the warmth and charm exuded by this home. Wide entry opens to gracious living room with a beautiful floor to ceiling stone fireplace; definitely the focal point of the home and perfect for snuggling in and warming up on cold winter nights! Gourmet Kitchen featuring large island, tons of custom cabinetry and ss appliances! Culinary enthusiasts will enjoy the pot filler and double convection oven that is also a microwave. Make the backyard your own tranquil place with views of Texas sunsets and a small pond that can add a touch of natural beauty to life. (pond holds water in spring-maturing with each year) Embrace the opportunity to slow down, breathe the fresh air and soak in the slow pace of country living!
